data.title: Did you know that Wilhelm Röntgen was unfairly expelled from school after being accused of producing a caricature of one of the teachers,...
data.meta_description:
7,765 likes, 31 comments - nobelprize_org on March 27, 2022: "Did you know that Wilhelm Röntgen was unfairly expelled from school after being accused of producing a caricature of one of the teachers, which was in fact done by someone else.

He went onto discover X-rays and be awarded the very first Nobel Prize in Physics.

Learn more by clicking the link in bio. 

Illustration: Ola Skogäng. 

#NobelPrize #science".
